        Nearest City:


   Site Amenities:

     None

                          Boat Launch Type:

                            1 Concrete Plank Ramp

   Car Parking Facilities:

     10 Gravel Spaces

                          Trailer Parking Facilities:

                            20 Gravel Spaces

        Seasonal Limitations:

        No known limitations

        Tidal or Water Limitations:

        yes - the river level may become too high to use the boat ramp.

        Driving Directions:

        From I-5 at Exit 32 (Kalama River Rd), W .3 mi on Kalama River Rd; L
        at unmarked gravel Rd across from Tradewinds Rd; go 300 ft. to ramp.
        Site Description:

        The lower portion of the ramp has developed undermining erosion
        problems. The ramp is protected by rip-rap and bank-cuts. The
        parking area has about 6 inches of silt from past flooding.


   Up Arrow to Map   8. Boat Launch (Kalama)

